text: David Dvořáček (born June 4, 1992) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Sparta Praha of the Czech Extraliga. Dvořáček made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Sparta Praha during the 2014-15 Czech Extraliga season.
